### Create a new poll
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/polls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the best JS framework?",
  "options": ["react", "vue", "svelte", "angular"]
}

### Get all polls
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/polls

### Get a single poll
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/polls/68a588f6032a0e5c2d4c9b11

### Vote on Poll
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/votes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pollId": "68a588f6032a0e5c2d4c9b11",
  "option": "react",
  "voter": "narda@example.com"
}

### View results for a poll
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/votes/PASTE_VALID_ID_HERE
